These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-1::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, cranberry, kale, lemon, plum, potato
House: ranch-style, cottage, art-deco, palace, tower, cape-cod, gothic-revival
 1. the ranch-style house is the person eating asparagus##1
 2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 3. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
 4. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
 5. the ranch-style house is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
 7. the cottage house is on the right of the palace house##1
 8. the person eating kale is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
 9. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
10. the person eating lemon is the cape-cod house##1
11. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
12. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
13. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
14. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
15. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
16. the person eating kale is the cottage house##1
17. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
18. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6     |      7      |
| Food    | potato    | lemon  | plum       | asparagus | artichoke | cranberry | kale        |
| House   | tower | cape-cod | art-deco | ranch-style    | gothic-revival   | palace   | cottage |

