There 7 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, cabbage, carrot, pepper, radish, zucchini
 1. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
 2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 3. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
 6. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
10. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
11. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating radish##1
12. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growslily##1
13. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
14. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
15. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating broccoli##1
16. the person eating broccoli is the person who growsmarigold##1
17. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3    |    4    |       5       |     6     |    7     |
