18. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |       5       |      6       |   7    |
| Job     | dancer   | musician | architect | scientist | nurse         | photographer | pilot  |
| Cigar   | dunhill | blend   | chaman  | siglo   | fonseca | game   | alhambra |

