11. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
15. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
